They've done a bit of a 180, not a complete 180, maybe.

03:38.980 --> 03:39.900
Pick an angle here.

03:39.900 --> 03:40.400
Come on.

03:40.400 --> 03:40.980
Maybe a 90.

03:40.980 --> 03:41.700
OK.

03:41.700 --> 03:43.060
It's a pivot.

