17:07.420 --> 17:08.500
So here's the thing.

17:08.500 --> 17:11.820
Windows doesn't really boot like that anymore.

17:11.820 --> 17:14.220
Microsoft was really involved in the whole UEFI thing

17:14.220 --> 17:17.140
