25:24.020 --> 25:28.060
The Raspberry Pi 4 is, it feels like if you're not

25:28.060 --> 25:30.020
super familiar with the Raspberry Pis,

25:30.020 --> 25:32.940
it looks like a regular Raspberry Pi,

25:32.940 --> 25:35.420
maybe slightly larger.

