27:52.820 --> 27:55.100
where a computer that takes a little while to open up

27:55.100 --> 27:57.340
your web browser, sometimes it takes a while for the next tab

27:57.340 --> 27:59.700
to open, it feels like a spinning rust machine.

27:59.700 --> 28:01.620
