28:01.620 --> 28:03.300
you may get away with a Raspberry Pi.

28:03.300 --> 28:06.180
For most of the history of mankind's computing,

28:06.180 --> 28:09.820
totally usable if you're a desktop power user,

28:09.820 --> 28:10.740
you're going to hate it.

28:10.740 --> 28:11.620
Yeah.

