What was interesting is when it came to a lot of CPU tests,

30:26.780 --> 30:35.140
the Raspberry Pi 4 would lag behind a moderate 2011 Intel

30:35.140 --> 30:35.780
system.

30:35.780 --> 30:39.620
I compared it to quad cores and dual core systems.

30:39.620 --> 30:41.980
