30:41.980 --> 30:46.980
the Raspberry Pi 4 was notably slower.

30:46.980 --> 30:48.460
Right, not out of this world, not

30:48.460 --> 30:50.860
a different order of magnitude, but noticeably slower.

30:50.860 --> 30:53.460
